name: 丹尼斯·奥伊
introduction: Denis Ooi is an international actor best known for his roles in the feature film "Dumb Money" (Sony) and his recurring appearances in "Bridge and Tunnel" (MGM+) His other recent credits include roles in "Fleishman is in Trouble" (FX/HULU), "The Peripheral" (AMAZON), "FBI" (NBC), "Billions" (SHOWTIME), "New Amsterdam" (NBC), "Law and Order: Organized Crime" (NBC), "The Equalizer" (CBS), "Blindspot" (NBC), and "Power Book III: Rise of Kanan."Denis Ooi's background is marked by his mixed heritage; his mother has European roots, while his father's family originates from Singapore, Malaysia and South China. He holds citizenship in the United States, Switzerland, and the United Kingdom and was raised in both England and Switzerland.
